{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/fclask","slide":1,"text":"About 45 seconds. One contribution I am especially proud of is the backend for data source versioning. A privacy dashboard should not only show the current state of a dataset. It should preserve earlier states and their risk results, so changes remain auditable. My implementation creates immutable snapshots while also handling duplicate and concurrent updates safely."}
