{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/4lwhuy","slide":2,"text":"About 55 seconds. Before this feature, a data source was just one mutable database record. Every edit replaced the previous state. For a privacy dashboard, that is a problem because the risk level and metadata may change over time. My goal was therefore to keep the current record simple for normal use, but append an immutable snapshot whenever its meaningful state changes."}
