{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/6cfdqk","slide":5,"text":"About 55 seconds. I am proud of this contribution because it is not only a visible feature. It creates trustworthy evidence. The snapshots make changes auditable, transaction and locking make the ordering reliable, and historical risk results remain stable even if the assessment algorithm changes later. For me, this was a good example of turning a user story into a robust backend design."}